        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/mujam-al-ahadith-al-mutabara:2:13:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/2/13/2",
        "text": [
          ": قال ابوعبدالله عليه السلام: كل شئ يكون فيه حرام وحلال فهو لك حلال ابدا حتى تعرف الحرام منه بعينه فتدعه"
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.ammaar-muslim": [
            "2. [2/93] al-Faqih and al-Tahdhib: From Ibn Mahbub from Abdallah b. Sinan who said: Abu Abdillah عليه السلام said: everything which has both Halal and Haram [elements mixed into it] then it is Halal for you forever until you know the Haram in it specifically so you abandon it."
          ]
        }
      }
